data.value:
Backup/synchronize your data for Windows, Linux.
Import photos from phone through WI-FI and more.

Features:
- Incremental backup with deduplication of files and WebDAV, S3-compatible, NFS, Azure Blob, SFTP, FTPS, SMB/CIFS transports support;
- Synchronization of files between devices wey dey use centralized storage and versioning support;
- Import media - Import audios, photos, videos from SD Card of camera, recorder; photos and videos from your phone through WI-FI through FTPS Server application wey dey use template file names or through;
- Console for automation scheduling;
- AES-256 encryption.

Platforms: Windows 11 x64, ARM64 or Ubuntu 24+.
